%e A327921 Some zeros are:
%e A327921 n = 1:  2*cos(2*Pi*1/4) = 0 = s(1),
%e A327921 n = 2:  2*cos(2*Pi*1/4) = 2 = s(2) (diameter/R),
%e A327921 n = 3:  2*cos(2*Pi*1/12) = -2*cos(2*Pi*5/12) = sqrt(3) = s(3),
%e A327921 n = 5:  2*cos(2*Pi*1/20) = -2*cos(2*Pi*9/20) = sqrt(2 + phi),
%e A327921         2*cos(2*Pi*3/20) = -2*cos(2*Pi*7/20) = sqrt(phi - 3) = s(5),
%e A327921 with the golden ratio phi = A001622,
%e A327921 n = 10: 2*cos(2*Pi*1/5) = phi - 1 = s(10),  -2*cos(2*Pi*2/5) = -phi.
